author: 4 Ever Green
description:
Some dogs aren’t just pets they’re living history. From Pharaohs’ sacred companions to temple guardians in the Himalayas, these are the oldest dog breeds still alive today.
They fought beside warriors, were mummified with kings, and even climb trees like cats. Some are older than the pyramids and they still walk among us.

🌍 Featuring:
✅ Saluki
✅ Tibetan Mastiff
✅ Basenji
✅ Chow Chow
✅ Samoyed
✅ Xoloitzcuintli
✅ Akita Inu
✅ Afghan Hound… and more!
Watch till the end to discover the oldest dog breed on Earth.


#AncientDogs #OldestDogBreeds #4EverGreen
title: 15 Oldest Dog Breeds That Ruled Beside Ancient Civilizations
